Class User

  • java.lang.Object
    • io.analytics.domain.User

    java.io.Serializable, org.springframework.security.core.userdetails.UserDetails

    public class User
extends java.lang.Object
implements org.springframework.security.core.userdetails.UserDetails
    This represents a User of our application as it exists in the database. This is a User specific to our application, and is different from a Google account user, for example.
